title: Bottom View Toolbar
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The main view toolbar is now a separate bar at the bottom of each tiddler, but actions can also be added to the title bar. Use the tags $:/tags/ViewToolbar/Title, $:/tags/ViewToolbar/BottomLeft and $:/tags/ViewToolbar/BottomRight instead of $:/tags/ViewToolbar.

The action button icons are replaced with Material Icons.